                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. de Stoeckl</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                        Seward</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">New York</hi>,</placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1867-05-15">
                            <hi rend="italic">May</hi> 15, 1867</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">William H. Seward:</hi>
                </p>
                <p>Just received the following telegram from St. Petersburg:</p>
                <p>“Treaty ratified. Bodisco carries it back and leaves immediately.</p>
                <p rend="right">“GORTOHACOW.”</p>
                <p>I shall be in Washington tomorrow.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>STOECKL.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
